Name: JiraFire
Version: 0.1
Synopsis: Provides a customizable personal jira burndown
Authors: Nathan Holland <nholland94@gmail.com>
License: LGPL with OCaml linking exception
Description: Jira burndown allows you to create a personal burndown from a board an queue up tasks.

OASISFormat: 0.4
BuildTools: ocamlbuild
Plugins: META (0.4), DevFiles (0.4)

Executable "jira_fire"
  Path: src
  MainIs: main.ml
  BuildDepends:
    core, curl, yojson, base64, redis
